quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  44,30,Soni chisimu twajokwele ŵanache ŵa Israila ku ilagasyo yakwalusya
  44,31,"Yakuumila kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakulikwesya, (soni jumpepe) mwa akusumba mpika"
  44,32,Soni twasagwile ŵanganyao (ŵanache ŵa Israila) pa umanyilisi kuipunda iwumbe yosope (yandaŵi jao)
  44,33,Ni twapele ilosyo yayaliji nkati mwakwe mayeso gakuonechela
  44,34,Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (Makuraishi) akutiji
  44,35,"“Pangali chinechakwe ikaŵeje chiwa chetu chandanda (pechi chatukuwaga chachili chipelela chetu), soni nganituŵa uwwe ŵakwimusyidwa (m’malembe).”"
  44,36,“Basi ikani nao achatati ŵetu (ŵaŵawile kalakala) nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona (kuti kwana kwimuka m’malembe).”
  44,37,"Ana ŵanganyao (Makuraishi) niŵali ŵambone, kapena ŵandu ŵa Tubba‘i (ŵa ku Yemeni), ni aŵala ŵapaujo pao? Twajonasile (wosope ŵeneo), chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵakuleŵa"
  44,38,Soni Uwwe nganitugumba mawunde ni mataka kwisa soni yaili chilikati chakwe mwamasanje
  44,39,"Nganituigumba yele iŵiliyi ikaŵeje mwakuonaonape, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ngakumanyilila"
  44,40,"Chisimu lisiku lyachiilanyo, ni ndema jao wosope ŵene (jajiŵichidwe jakwapela ipotesi)"
  44,41,"Lisiku lyangakamuchisya jwaulongo kwa nnongo n’jakwe chindu chilichose, nambo soni ŵanganyao ngasakulupusyidwa"
  44,42,"Ikaŵeje ŵatachatendela chanasa Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe ni jwali Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwachanasa channope"